    <subsection>
        <title>
            5.1 - Laplace Transforms
        </title>
        
        <p>
            In this section, we will learn to compute Laplace transforms. 
            <ol>
                <li><p> Watch <url href="https://youtu.be/l8gr3sFc--A">🎥 Video 5.1.1</url> (2:36). </p></li>
                <li><p> 🎯 <alert> Practice: </alert> Verify all of the transforms showin in Theorem 7.1.1 (pg. 258). Then use these identities on preoblems 20-36 (evens) from Exercises 7.1 (pg. 261). </p></li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </subsection>

    <subsection>
        <title>
            5.2 - Inverse Laplace Transforms
        </title>
        
        <p>
            In this section, we will learn to compute inverse Laplace transforms.
