            <ol>
                <li><p> Watch <url href="https://youtu.be/sb3A2awuY78"> 🎥 Video 5.3.1 </url> (9:56). </p></li>
                <li><p> Complete <url href="https://canvas.svsu.edu/courses/93320/quizzes/352528">✅ Checkpoint 5.3.1 </url>. </p></li>
                <li><p> 🎯 <alert> Practice: </alert> Problems 1-19 (alternating odds), 37-47 (odds) in Exercises 7.3 (pg. 278). </p></li> 
                <li><p> 🎯 <alert> Practice: </alert> Problems 1, 5, 19-29 (odds), 49-53 (odds) in Exercises 7.4 (pgs. 289-290). </p></li> 
            </ol>
        </p>
    </subsection>

